OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773843069
OL,3,CPolice officer who binned mobile phone
OL,4,Cevidence jailed
OL,6,FA police officer has been jailed for
OL,7,Fbinning her mobile phone just before
OL,8,Fshe was due to be questioned by anti-
OL,9,Fcorruption officers.
OL,11,FFormer Lancashire Police Constable
OL,12,FSamarah Kamal was jailed for nine
OL,13,Fmonths and two weeks after she
OL,14,Fadmitted to perverting the course of
OL,15,Fjustice on 12 February 2026.
OL,17,FThe force said the 27-year-old from
OL,18,FPreston "fell well short of what the
OL,19,Fpublic would expect of a serving
OL,20,Fpolice officer" during her time in the
OL,21,FEast Response Investigations Team.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
