OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773843069
OL,3,CPolice officer who binned mobile phone
OL,4,Cevidence jailed
OL,6,FAnti-corruption officers tried to
OL,7,Fcontact Kamal on 24 July 2023, but
OL,8,Ffound she had phoned in sick to work.
OL,10,FOfficers spoke to Kamal at 15:02 and
OL,11,Farranged to meet her, and she was
OL,12,Farrested when she arrived at 15:11.
OL,14,FKamal was searched along with her
OL,15,Fhome, and it was discovered that in
OL,16,Fthe nine minutes between speaking to
OL,17,Fthe investigating officer and arriving
OL,18,Fat their location, she had thrown away
OL,19,Fher mobile phone which could have
OL,20,Fcontained evidence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773843069
OL,3,CPolice officer who binned mobile phone
OL,4,Cevidence jailed
OL,6,FKamal, of Fletcher Road, Preston, was
OL,7,Fcharged with perverting the course of
OL,8,Fjustice and pleaded guilty at
OL,9,FLiverpool Crown Court.
OL,11,FKamal was dismissed from Lancashire
OL,12,FConstabulary following an Accelerated
OL,13,FMisconduct Hearing in 2025, and has
OL,14,Fbeen indefinitely barred from working
OL,15,Ffor the police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
