PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1773843069
OL,3,CPolice officer who binned mobile phone
OL,4,Cevidence jailed
OL,6,FDet Supt Pete Reil, Head of Lancashire
OL,7,FPolice's Professional Standards
OL,8,FDepartment, said: "Samarah Kamal's
OL,9,Fdishonest conduct fell well short of
OL,10,Fwhat the public would expect of a
OL,11,Fserving police officer.
OL,13,F"Quite rightly, it has resulted in a
OL,14,Fcriminal conviction and dismissal from
OL,15,Fher privileged role as a police
OL,16,Fofficer."
